WEBVTT

00:00:09.145 --> 00:00:17.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At the start of the day,
with the sun yet to rise,

00:00:17.562 --> 00:00:22.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are making our way
with the sleep in our eyes,

00:00:22.354 --> 00:00:26.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we pray.

00:00:26.437 --> 00:00:34.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are there with a smile
for the people we meet.

00:00:34.895 --> 00:00:43.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Some may stop for a while,
some pass by on the street, but we stay.

00:00:43.562 --> 00:00:52.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s the life that we choose;
For Jehovah we live.

00:00:52.104 --> 00:01:00.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And whatever he asks, we will do.

00:01:00.770 --> 00:01:09.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the work we endure,
Whether sunshine or rain.

00:01:09.562 --> 00:01:21.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s a way we can say ev’ry day:
“I love you.”

00:01:26.812 --> 00:01:35.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At the end of the day,
with the sun sinking low,

00:01:35.604 --> 00:01:40.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Feeling happy and tired,
in our heart there’s a glow,

00:01:40.020 --> 00:01:44.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we pray.

00:01:44.229 --> 00:01:52.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s a life that we love,
always giving our best.

00:01:52.770 --> 00:02:01.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And Jehovah we thank,
for by him we are blessed ev’ry day.

00:02:01.395 --> 00:02:09.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s the life that we choose;
For Jehovah we live.

00:02:09.937 --> 00:02:18.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And whatever he asks, we will do.

00:02:18.520 --> 00:02:27.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the work we endure,
Whether sunshine or rain.

00:02:27.187 --> 00:02:41.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s a way we can say ev’ry day:
“I love you.”

